How to run the simulator

./run mapdir/ [arg]

where mapdir/ is the folder where the xml definition of the map is located along with the gentrips and simulate script

arguments
-u # ---percentage vehicles using the system
-tp # ---generate new vehicle spwaning times from the OD matrix in gentrips.py with # percentage busses 
-c # ---only work if tp is given set the congestion level recommend between 0.4 - 2.0 default 1.4
-g ---system starts with GUI
-n ---rebuild the map
-o ---set output of the testresults
